text: I'm Jason Blackman CIO here at car sales
car sales is the largest online
automotive motorcycle and marine
classifieds business in Australia we are
also a global organization with a
presence in Asia and South America
including South Korea Brazil Chile and
Mexico to enable this global expansion
we now have a cloud centric technology
platform our cloud journey started back
in 2013 and we recently moved entirely
to the cloud one of the key benefits is
that our rate of deployment has
significantly increased it used to be
just twice weekly but we are now at a
few hundred per day this allows us to
quickly build and deliver products to
our customers car sales adoption of
cloud ready technology platform has
resulted in improved cloud utilization
saving costs and increased development
efficiency to improve business
efficiency fraud detection and to
deliver a better overall consumer
experience at scale we have started our
AI journey AWS machine learning services
such as deep learning and sage maker has
helped our team build AI based
technology more efficiently without the
need for us to worry about the
infrastructure we are always looking for
ways to innovate and to make our process
more efficient there are many more AWS
services like personalized and
reinforcement learning that we're very
keen to use there are so many
opportunities to work with AWS early in
the development of our products helping
us to deliver real innovation for our
customers now and into the future
